Spider-Man has faced some _amazing_ foes on the big screen, but which baddies are truly _spectacular_ and which ones are just... _meh_? In this episode of the **Major Issues Podcast**, we’re bringing back **Tier Factor**, our totally scientific and not-at-all biased ranking system, to stack up every live-action Spider-Man villain from _Goblin-glorious_ to _Rhino-ridiculous_.

Will Willem Dafoe’s Green Goblin _finish it_ at the top? Does Topher Grace’s Venom even stand a chance? And where do we put whatever _The Amazing Spider-Man 2_ was doing? Join us as we web-sling through the best and worst of Spidey’s rogues, laugh at some questionable CGI choices, and probably argue way too much about Jamie Foxx’s Electro.

Suit up, because with _great rankings_ comes _great responsibility_! 🎙🕷️🔥

